<div class="page-header" id="index">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <h1>Statsmile</h1>
      <p class="lead">Simple and intuitive service statistics for Dota 2.</p>
      <p><a href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#loginModal" class="btn btn-lg btn-main-style">Sign in with Steam ID</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row" id="features">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <span class="batch batch-logo uniF161"></span>
      <h3>Easy and simple</h3>
      <p>Simple and intuitive interface based on the popular framework Bootstrap will allow you to quickly and easily search for and watch your matches in Dota 2.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <span class="batch batch-logo uniF0AE"></span>
      <h3>Bookmarks</h3>
      <p>At any time you can add statistics of the match in the bookmarks to mark their keyword order not to lose their epic moments.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <span class="batch batch-logo uniF150"></span>
      <h3>Share your friends</h3>
      <p>Share links to the statistics of his matches. Single match, your profile, records and more.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <ul class="head-links">
        <li><a href="#">Blog</a></li>
        <li>{{#link-to 'faq'}}FAQ{{/link-to}}</li>
        <li>{{#link-to 'privacy'}}Privacy{{/link-to}}</li>
        <li>{{#link-to 'status'}}Status API{{/link-to}}</li>
        <li class="version">Version 2.0 Alpha</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="loginModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
        <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Sign in with Steam ID</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p class="text-center"><span class="batch batch-huge uniF15A"></span></p>
        <p>Before we begin, we would like to know that your games are available for public.
          If you have been previously authorized - can continue, but remember: if you want to have all your games were
          available - do not turn off the option "Share Match History".</p>
        <p class="text-warning">If you're here for your first time, please make sure that the option "Share Match History" is enabled in
            the settings of the client Dota 2.</p>
        <p>Ready?</p>
        <p class="text-center">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Wait I need to prepare!</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-success">I'm ready. Let's start</button>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>